fields.name: Running Workout plan
fields.description: Attain your next personal best running time with our running program; that our personal trainers will tailor the program to your specific goals. The program will run for four months; split into four quarters which focus on your running form, pace, endurance, flexibility, and recovery methods.

fields.name: Weight Lifting Plan
fields.description: Boost your gains with our very own weight lifting program, which is designed specifically for improving your compound lifts such as the deadlift and bench press. The program lasts for a period of three months; focusing on power, endurance, lift-technique, form, and others.

fields.name: Yoga plan
fields.description:
Achieve Zen levels of flexibility with our yoga plan, which in consultation with our yoga instructors is tailored to your individual ability. 
The program duration lasts for a month, members can extend unlimited times if they would like.

fields.name: Body Weight Plan
fields.description:
Purchase our bodyweight plan and allow us to plan your next three months with workouts that you can do from anywhere with your body and a small space, being the only pieces of equipment you need.
The plan will focus on all upper, lower body, and core exercises.

fields.name: Hiit plan
fields.description:
Short on time and need to complete your workouts as soon as possible? Burn fat fast with our HIIT training plan, each workout lasting only thirty minutes and is jam-packed with exercises that gives you a great burn. 

The program duration lasts 6 months

fields.name: Gym Ankle socks
